Stages in Koine development {<inc> Seigel9?, 201} 

PROCESS <proc00>    STAGE <state00>
Koineization        pre-koine
stabilization       stable koine
expansion           expanded koine
nativization        nativized koine


nativization of koine at dif stages--(can inc pidgin as input)
(202)

PROCESS        STAGE
Koineization   pre-koine      pre-koine      pre-koine
stabilization      :          stable koine   stable koine
expansion          :               :         exp'd koine
nativization   nat'd koine    nat'd koine    nat'd koine

examples:      Trinidad       Guyanese       Greek Koine
              Bhojpuri       Bhojpuri

